<item>
            <title>[LU-16192] Recommended patches for target_version: 2.13.0.0 and target_version: 2.12.8.0</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16192</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;br/&gt;
We are running tversion 2.13.0.0 in our Production Lustre Environment and ran into the soft lock LDLM DOM issue.&lt;br/&gt;
We have however implemented the work around to clear the soft locks on the clients in order to keep the environment up and running.&lt;br/&gt;
Can you recommend any patches we can apply on version 2.13.0.0 and can they be applied while the system is running as i did read on a wiki that making changes to the file-system parameter will require the file-system to not be active?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note&lt;br/&gt;
If the number of service threads is changed while the file system is running, the change may not take effect until the file system is stopped and rest.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is version 2.12.8.0 also impacted by this bug and should we apply any patches?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Playpen and Production</environment>
