                            <comment id="348007" author="adilger" created="Tue, 27 Sep 2022 08:34:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Note that we do not make any maintenance releases for 2.13.0.  The 2.15 release is a Long Term Support (LTS) release, and receives fixes. The current maintenance release is 2.15.1. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is also a 2.12.9 maintenance release that contains a number of fixes over 2.12.8. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
